@api
Feature: Registering a new user account via API # features/api_register.feature:2

  Scenario: I successfully register a new user through the API   # features/api_register.feature:4
    Given I am a new visitor without an account                  # features/steps/api_register_steps.py:7
    When I register with valid personal and contact details      # features/steps/api_register_steps.py:12
    Then my account should be successfully registered            # features/steps/api_register_steps.py:18
    And I should be able to retrieve my account details by email # features/steps/api_register_steps.py:26

@ui
Feature: Register and order as a new user # features/register.feature:2

  Scenario: I register during checkout and successfully place an order                  # features/register.feature:4
    Given I navigate to the home page                                                   # features/steps/home_page_steps.py:5
    When I add products to my cart                                                      # features/steps/home_page_steps.py:12
    And I go to my cart                                                                 # features/steps/home_page_steps.py:17
    Then I should see my cart                                                           # features/steps/cart_page_steps.py:5
    When I proceed to checkout                                                          # features/steps/cart_page_steps.py:11
    And I choose to register a new account                                              # features/steps/cart_page_steps.py:16
    And I sign up and create my account                                                 # features/steps/login_page_steps.py:10
    Then I should see the message "ACCOUNT CREATED!" and I am logged in                 # features/steps/acc_created_steps.py:5
    When I go back to my cart                                                           # features/steps/home_page_steps.py:22
    And I confirm the checkout                                                          # features/steps/cart_page_steps.py:21
    Then I should see my address and order details                                      # features/steps/checkout_page_steps.py:5
    When I leave a comment and place my order                                           # features/steps/checkout_page_steps.py:11
    And I provide my payment details                                                    # features/steps/payment_page_steps.py:6
    Then I should see success message "Congratulations! Your order has been confirmed!" # features/steps/payment_done_steps.py:5
    When I delete my account                                                            # features/steps/payment_done_steps.py:11
    Then I should see the message "Account Deleted!"                                    # features/steps/deleteacc_page_steps.py:5
    And I finish by clicking Continue                                                   # features/steps/deleteacc_page_steps.py:11

